          "description": "String input of carrier_name in order to search for all locations that take at least one plan from a given insurance carrier.\nFind the individual valid carrier_name values from the insurance objects returned in the Insurances Reference Endpoint.\nNote: This input must be an exact string match to work",
          "example": "Aetna"
        },
